creator: TRAINERIZE
descriptionHtml: Bump Runner by Relentless Runners, LLC, has programs designed for the hopeful mama, expecting mama, and recovering postpartum mama, all looking to continue running. Every program's mission is to strengthen your pelvic floor and deep core to keep you strong throughout your pregnancy and postpartum journey to keep you laced up and doing what you love, RUNNING! All programs were created by a certified pre and postnatal fitness specialist and certified running coach. Be sure to check out our website at: relentlessrunners.com

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Consistency is key with this release! Introducing habit streaks and achievement badges—a new way to motivate clients to build healthy habits! Clients can create habit winning streaks by completing a habit every day that it’s scheduled into their calendars. As their streak continues to grow, they'll unlock special achievement badges at various milestones. 

As always, we've also made some back-end upgrades and bug fixes to make your experience even better.
